description: Mama Kim and her staff have been bringing culinary delights to Sacramento for over 15 years. Mama Kim on the Go is the first food truck to have received a slow food award for their commitment to quality and local support. We specialize in events large or small and will customize the menu to best serve your event. Whether an intimate sit down dinner in your home or a 300 plus charity event, Mama Kim Cooks superior service and astounding tastes will bring anyone back for more.
name: Mama Kim
